expenses incurred in bringing the civil action, and provides for the information to be
provided within an application for injunction that is filed pursuant to proposed law.
Proposed law provides for certain time periods where enforcement against the political
subdivision is not applicable.
Proposed law provides for duties of the state fire marshal.
Present law (R.S. 44:4.1(B)(6)) provides for a list of exemptions from public disclosure of
certain information contained in present law (Title 13 of the La. R.S.).
